{"tid":1471368,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推爆!] 一齊守護法治，要求入境處捉拿付國豪+徐錦煬，恢復社會秩序!","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T10:02:25.000Z","uid":265069,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3d955f3efc6deeb3187f23f15042f397c7d7c866","tid":1471368,"uid":265069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9A5M5ah.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9A5M5ah.png&h=1a223d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片所示，<ins><strong>付國豪</strong></ins>既入境標籤上面寫住訪客批准逗留至2019年08月13日,佢係大約凌晨12點出現機場,已經係違反左入境條例,係過期居留。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第115章 入境條例 第41節:<br />\n任何人違反對他有效的逗留條件，即屬犯罪，經定罪後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可處第5級罰款及監禁2年</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<ins><strong>徐錦煬</strong></ins>係深圳福田公安，經巴打於網上查證，證實徐錦煬為深圳福田公安。而一個廣東省，只有一個徐錦煬! 並唔係撞名! 而公安係香港執行職務，亦同樣有違金入境條例!<br />\n<br />\n根 據 香 港 法 例 《 入 境 規 例 》 ( 第 115A 章 ) 第 2 (1) 條 的 規 定 ， 給 予 某 人 以 訪 客 身 分 在 香 港 入 境 的 准 許 ， 須 受 下 述 逗 留 條 件 規 限 ：<br />\n該 人 不 得 接 受 有 薪 或 無 薪 的 僱 傭 工 作 ；<br />\n該 人 不 得 開 辦 或 參 與 任 何 業 務 ； <br />\n<br />\n不論以上兩位人兄遭受待遇如何，佢地已經干犯咗香港法律。中國人民最重視守法，佢地一個逾期居留，一個來港執行職務，絕對係無法無天! 公安入境香港，警方好可能又會包庇，話睇唔到實質證據、入境事務交由入境處調查。今次違反逗留條件，事關入境處責任，佢地責無旁貸!如果入境處選擇無視，就係任由香港以外司法管轄區踐踏一國兩制，監管香港事務，絕不能容忍! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下為舉報方法:<br />\n<br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線：(852) 2824 1551<br />\n(舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號)傳真：<br />\n(852) 2824 1166電郵：<br />\nanti_crime@immd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n重法治，護香江! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎大家打電話或以電郵形式投訴有關個案!"},{"pid":"22c3b3d8c396772def3d4c25df0ef830e7452e45","tid":1471368,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeBHOk.jpg&h=4d624e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7KeuxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&h=6eb7f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95FtyZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95FtyZg.jpg&h=ecc3ae69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caConSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaConSC.jpg&h=d1559671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f54d1376932c626efadf681b407c68cd36982fdb","tid":1471368,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35418525684621c25cc29ca1f023fe9fed7ef231","tid":1471368,"uid":213993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"57b1a0bf333b3209a214f7867aba62f70a012d2c","tid":1471368,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9fc349fbe0c0cc97fe457c02c2a183b8c09374fe","tid":1471368,"uid":293947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"張警察卡片有冇玄機?"},{"pid":"ab9e58420295390df206f996ec8babaf05056451","tid":1471368,"uid":124030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90aff600c378a416199da10038abc8940bf205c2","tid":1471368,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b00280d4384fae934af48141cebbc38f49292d4","tid":1471368,"uid":280582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"道歉係處理關公 唔理人做鬼揞眼做<br />\n道歉係我哋有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋敢道歉 警察敢嗎？<br />\n不完美可接受會改變</span></span> 呢句係popo教我講嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打大佬啦各位 大佬放鬼出關公呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不割但要智取捉鬼打關公<br />\n捉到鬼selfie求放朋友圈 多謝參與</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地敢道歉 警察你敢嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470560</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDLEEQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDLEEQu.jpg&h=57a4d3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZxSZQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZxSZQA.jpg&h=1e282855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0709181c25157a4f82ffad448e8abf840c0d3363","tid":1471368,"uid":265069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2eVejD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2eVejD.png&h=a9d9e0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊心護法治，關注香江事!<br />\n以下為電郵template!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">---------------------</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入境處部門:<br />\n<br />\n按昨日各媒體所得資料，一名中國籍男子付國豪先生的入境標籤上面寫有訪客，其批准逗留日期至2019年08月13日。該名男子於2019年8月14日凌晨出現機場，已屬違反入境條例，為過期居留。 據媒體資料所得，其證件號碼為C71032238。入境標籤右側印有369791607。<br />\n<br />\n另一位中國藉男子徐錦煬先生，經網上查證，證實徐錦煬為深圳福田公安。而廣東省以內只有一位名為徐錦煬男子。 公安於香港執行職務，同樣有違入境條例之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n根 據 香 港 法 例 《 入 境 規 例 》 ( 第 115A 章 ) 第 2 (1) 條 的 規 定 ， 給 予 某 人 以 訪 客 身 分 在 香 港 入 境 的 准 許 ， 須 受 下 述 逗 留 條 件 規 限 ： 該 人 不 得 接 受 有 薪 或 無 薪 的 僱 傭 工 作 ； 該 人 不 得 開 辦 或 參 與 任 何 業 務 ；<br />\n<br />\n逾期居留香港及於香港執行職務均顯然干犯香港法律。 內地公安跨境於香港執行職務更屬違反一國兩制，入境處必須嚴正跟進此類情況，並檢視會否有任何漏洞可予公安來港執行職務  。本人重視法治作為香港之核心價值，以上情況，實不可不察。本人希望此個案能嚴肅跟進，並予本人個案編號以作日後跟進查核。<br />\n<br />\n守護香江，你我有責，望入境處秉公處理! 謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n熱心市民<br />\n陳先生上"},{"pid":"b8f3e3f33e2e69ac445f7060f88fbf1952477372","tid":1471368,"uid":265069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"大大力pish"},{"pid":"ee3cbe01f1c7d5f55840a7afbd4c6474b62a8a5b","tid":1471368,"uid":224859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<br />\n光復香港"},{"pid":"c58686de6a4c71e8a92191011b58b35c3bce201f","tid":1471368,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f94d477189311e59cf706397ca8676d42dba43","tid":1471368,"uid":243955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"瘋狂推進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e020fed41c04268bb6ea7515a452a8b17ba4e0d6","tid":1471368,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b69428e7b6eedf79cf476fc8fc27dfba89dc93cb","tid":1471368,"uid":265211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"徐錦煬直頭係<span style=\"color: red;\">持攻擊性武器</span>啦<br />\n應該報警通輯佢<br />\n如果黑警認為鐳射筆係武器<br />\n兩碌木棍唔係武器<br />\n我日日帶兩碌出街"},{"pid":"a0b2954aeedca80ce08e9948f3e9c67827b71c62","tid":1471368,"uid":265069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69428e7b6eedf79cf476fc8fc27dfba89dc93cb","tid":1471